Imparative ways and declarative ways

# Imparative way
1. kubectl run nginx-pod --image=nginx:latest (Imparative way run the container in a pod) 
2. kubectl get pods (Imparative way to get the node information)
3. kubectl get pod nginx-pod -o wide (check the pod information)
4. kubectl delete pod nginx-pod (delete the pod)


# Declarative way
1. kubectl apply -f nginx-basic.yaml (Run the container declaratively in a pod)
2. kubectl describe pod nginx-pod (check the pod information)
3. kubectl exec -it nginx-pod bash (login bash in the pod)
4. kubectl exec -it nginx-pod -- sh (login sh in the pod shell mode)
5. kubectl get pod nginx-pod --show-labels -o wide (check the pod information)
6. kubectl get pods -o wide (check the node information)